sentences.english: Coruscant continued as the capital of the galaxy under this new regime.
sentences.chinese: 在這個新政權的統治下，科洛桑依然是銀河系的首都。

sentences.english: Vos voyaged to Coruscant to kill Senator Kaa, but Windu stopped Vos in time.

sentences.english: Episode II also features Weequays both on Tatooine, and in the lower levels of Coruscant.
sentences.chinese: 在《第二集》裏，塔圖因和科洛桑下層也有威奎人。

sentences.english: For a thousand generations Coruscant has been central to galactic affairs.
sentences.chinese: 一千代人以來，科洛桑始終是銀河事務的中心。

sentences.english: The UNIL campus is located on the shores of Lake Geneva.

sentences.english: Tavella is a researcher at the Federal Polytechnic School in Lausanne, Switzerland.

sentences.english: The calendar is based on the size and rotation of the planet Coruscant .

sentences.english: Over the next few years, the New Republic set up government on Coruscant.
sentences.chinese: 在隨後的幾年裏，新共和國在科洛桑設立政府。

sentences.english: Vast stretches of Coruscant's surface were laid to waste in the battle.
sentences.chinese: 科洛桑的表面在戰火中被大片大片地夷爲平地。

sentences.english: The New Republic retreated from Coruscant, leaving the splintering Imperial factions to war amongst themselves.
sentences.chinese: 新共和國撤出科洛桑，任憑帝國的各路軍閥互相內鬥。

sentences.english: In the end, Ben provided the location of the Saiy family to the Coruscant police.
sentences.chinese: 最後，本把賽伊家的地點告訴了科洛桑警方。

sentences.english: Seven years, the so-called law by shramanera precepts plunge in lausanne.
sentences.chinese: 七歲受沙彌戒，法號稱洛桑扎華。

sentences.english: This hope will push him for the change to materialize.

sentences.english: Two days after his arrival on Coruscant, Ghent had Ackbar cleared.
sentences.chinese: 根特抵達科洛桑兩天後，就爲阿克巴洗刷了罪名。

sentences.english: They had to reach Coruscant and get support for the Naboo.
sentences.chinese: 他們必須抵達科洛桑併爲納布贏得支持。
